      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           release   srt-rec                                          .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Incremento contatore record da chiudere         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-prn-ctr-rdc          .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione numero bolle da chiudere        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      07                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<G"                 to   v-edm
           move      09                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      30                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-prn-ctr-rdc        to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Riciclo su lettura sequenziale record [bft]     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     stp-srt-inp-100.
       stp-srt-inp-999.
           exit.

